title: It’s Expensive to be She
description: Casey and Danielle fly gorgeously solo this week. Casey is all abuzz over her new favorite show (also the worst show ever made) Selling OC. The girls dive into all that’s going on in the morass that is the Bravosphere. And most importantly, Danielle is incredibly upset that Kyle made Kathy sleep in a bunk bed. Enjoy!
